Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:39.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:43.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruhi established the SOS Brigade back in May...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:44.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and we are already in the month of June.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:47.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, during that period...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:51.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I happened to be involved in a world-cramping incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:53.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, let's just leave that aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:55.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today's story goes like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:56.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
