Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:00.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:03.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...nothing out of the ordinary ever happened...
