Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.65,0:01:07.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and I was able to enjoy a brief period of peace and tranquil tedium...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:09.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but oh, was it brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:10.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:14.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever her face lights up with that smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:17.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I end up being run ragged and exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:56.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say we're entering?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:57.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:04.92,HaruhiTitleOverlay,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs28\fad(490,460)\pos(294,409)}The Boredom of Haruhi Suzumiya
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:03.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ninth City Amateur Baseball Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:06.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So. Who's entering?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:07.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In this grass-lot baseball tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:12.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When you say we...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...are you including the rest of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:14.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000000&}- We'll need to find four more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:19.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As usual, she only hears the things she wants to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the rules for baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:24.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:26.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I joined the baseball team for a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I know the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was dead boring so I left immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:33.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So why do we have to participate in a tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...playing that dead boring baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:38.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a chance to make our existence known around the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:40.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If we win this tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:44.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...it could be a chance to make the name SOS Brigade stand on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:45.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a great opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:46.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:48.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a nice idea, Mikuru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:49.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:50.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:52.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Baseball sounds good, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:54.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, we're aiming for the championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single loss will be tolerated!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:58.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I really hate to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:02.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:06.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give your consent so cheerfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:09.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How about objecting every once in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:12.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds much more productive than walking around in search of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:14.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...aliens or UMAs, in my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So? When's the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:18.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:20.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The day after tomorrow!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:21.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:24.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I already turned in the application.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:28.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I named the team SOS Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:30.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be any mistakes in that department!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:34.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you planning on pulling together the other members from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:38.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just grab any bored-looking people we see walking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:40.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's serious about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:41.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:43.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You just sit tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:46.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First off, Taniguchi and Kunikida probably don't have anything to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:51.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruhi referred to classmates as objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:52.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:53.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Two more, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:55.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's okay, my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:58.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyone works, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:00.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:02.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Asahina-san's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:03.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's making me a little worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her friend from when and where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:07.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's from this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...someone I met from my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, allow me to join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:16.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can think of an acquaintance who has expressed interest in our...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:18.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,With that decided, let's start training!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:21.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Training!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Training, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:23.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right this instant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:24.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:25.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:26.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:34.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so we ended up participating in a tomfoolery of a baseball tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:38.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The answer is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Basically, Haruhi was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:42.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us use this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And your baseball equipment, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:50.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:54.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to practice baseball right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:55.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way, so leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:56.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell we're gonna leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:58.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just for a little while!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:05:59.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mikuru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A predictable adolescent response.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:09.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with a thousand hits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:12.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:23.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The future of the SOS Brigade rests upon that ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:28.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the first I've heard about our future resting upon such a minuscule ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:38.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:45.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't, Kyon-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:57.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're nice to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:58.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'll happen again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:02.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's retiring due to injury!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:09.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, the baseball team take the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:10.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:17.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:25.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was exactly one thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:29.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you counted to one thousand is what's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:30.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:34.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you make it rain on the day of the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge one that'll cancel the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:38.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:40.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it is not recommended.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:40.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:43.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Alterations to the local environmental data...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:47.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...may result in aftereffects to this planet's ecosystem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:49.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will these aftereffects last?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:51.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Between a few centuries and ten millennia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess we probably shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:56.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:02.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...here comes the day of the match!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It really didn't need to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:11.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Kyon-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:13.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard a lot about you from Mikuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:16.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:19.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my friend, Tsuruya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:20.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Taniguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:21.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:22.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kunikida.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:24.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:26.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't turn down a request from my buddy Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:27.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}Taniguchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}...and Kunikida-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}I'll remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:30.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:32.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}Let's have fun today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:35.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:38.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have that thing play baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:39.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}Hey, I watched a game the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:40.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thing" is a bit rude now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:40.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}The catcher...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:42.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That "thing" is still my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She introduced herself as an 11-year-old fifth grader.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:49.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a sweet little girl that it's hard to believe she's related to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:48.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}He hit a home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:53.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the baseball tournament we're entering is open to the general public!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:55.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't Little League!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that, Miss Haruhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:59.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is exactly why I brought my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our chance of victory is nil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Regardless, this is Haruhi we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watch us end up winning by accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That would definitely be a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we add a fifth grader into the mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:11.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}That's why I was really happy when I got to come along today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it'd be a joke if we won.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:13.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good enough handicap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:17.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel bad if we slaughtered the other team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Apparently, she seriously intends on winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:27.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...we haven't decided on a batting order or positions yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:28.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:30.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I already thought that through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any problems with deciding through this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:35.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One for batting order and one for field position.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'm the pitcher and lead-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:40.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So all you came up with was a method to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:41.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:43.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a democratic method.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:47.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They used lottery to choose their government in ancient Greece!
