Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:05.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...our first opponents are a college team, the Kamigahara Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:08.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The leading candidate to win this tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:10.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The game is called at ten runs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:14.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so now would be a good time to start packing up to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Play ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:34.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a totally weak pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:36.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you follow my lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go easy on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:42.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:45.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How dare you throw a real pitch at Asahina-san!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:47.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you hit her, there will immediate brawling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:48.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A brawling bash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:52.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:54.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Swing like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:56.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strikeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:59.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:01.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you swinging the bat!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:01.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:02.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:04.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strikeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:05.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hit the ball if you don't swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:09.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:10.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You better get a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:11.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're clean-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:14.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What can you possibly expect from a clean-up chosen through lottery?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:17.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruhi doubled off this pitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:21.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:31.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strikeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:32.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:34.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:33.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:38.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's shut them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:43.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:50.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:53.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strikeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:54.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice pitching!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:57.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Too easy! Too easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:03.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Foul ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:22.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If all you can throw is straight pitches in the strike zone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:23.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I got it! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...once they figure that out, you're going to get hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:28.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And our defense has more holes than an anthill in a savanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:27.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:28.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:29.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like a sieve!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fact that we only gave up two runs this inning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Great play!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:37.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...must be because the other team's goddess of victory is running late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:40.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I suppose that everyone wants to take it easy on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:38.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Way to go!
