Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:40.08,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fry40\1c&HFFFFFF\1a&H77&\frz0\fs28\pos(207,427)}Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:40.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Strikeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:43.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Continuing, our offensive in the top of the next inning came to an abrupt end...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Strikeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:42.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Strikeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:45.83,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fry40\1c&HFFFFFF\1a&H77&\frz-7\fs28\pos(211,232)}SOS Brigade
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:45.83,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fry40\1c&HFFFFFF\1a&H77&\frz-5\fs28\pos(145,266)}Kamigahara
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:45.83,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fry40\1c&HFFFFFF\1a&H77&\frz0\fs28\pos(207,427)}Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:46.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and our opponents easily built up their lead in the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It looks like we can end this in the next inning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:52.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a toughie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:57.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just getting the bat on the ball took everything I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we're going to need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Timeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:07.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:08.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzumiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:10.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:10.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000000&}- Stupid! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get undressed and change!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:17.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:17.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000000&}- Looking good there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:18.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:20.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:22.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It might go better with a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:27.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:27.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Start cheering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:30.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... How do I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:31.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:34.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Yell it loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:35.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:36.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hit the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:39.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:40.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:42.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strikeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can hit that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:45.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't expecting anything from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:03.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You better hit it this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:07.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000000&}- Mikuru! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:07.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Asahina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:11.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:12.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:14.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This! This!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:16.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:20.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she trying to reduce the magic points of the opposing pitcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:23.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear that she's giving a sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we ever decide on any signs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:26.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:30.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...she's probably signaling for a squeeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:33.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A squeeze towards first with two outs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:37.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even one of those lame duck managers could do a better job than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:43.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Presuming that Asahina-san's chances of hitting the ball are practically none...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:47.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...using a squeeze when least expected to surprise the opposing team...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:50.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...may possibly cause the infield to commit an error...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:56.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...or perhaps she thinks that even Asahina-san can at least manage to make contact with the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They've all figured it out though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:00.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:02.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strikeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:04.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:06.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here and buckle down for some pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is punishment! Punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:11.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let everyone look at your funny face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:18.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for giving signs that make no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:20.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just steal home by yourself or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have taken a bad turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:33.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want to hear it, but go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:37.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Closed space has appeared on a scale never before witnessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:40.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be expanding at an alarming rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:44.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Suzumiya-san retains her foul mood, it will continue to expand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:48.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and those will also continue to rampage around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because we're losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:52.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so full of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound as though it doesn't concern yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:57.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but this incident is largely due to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:16:01.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we drew lots to determine the batting order.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And consequently, you became clean-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not particularly happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You became the clean-up batter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:10.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...because Suzumiya-san desired it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:12.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:16.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...she was disappointed by your dismal performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:18.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:23.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...let us do everything possible to prevent the game from being called this inning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If the game ends now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:27.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...it will mean the end of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:28.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We must do all we can to hold them to two runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two outs. Runners on first and second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:43.97,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fry40\1c&HFFFFFF\1a&H77&\frz-7\fs28\pos(211,232)}SOS Brigade
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:43.97,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fry40\1c&HFFFFFF\1a&H77&\frz-5\fs28\pos(145,266)}Kamigahara
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:43.97,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fry40\1c&HFFFFFF\1a&H77&\frz0\fs28\pos(207,427)}Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:41.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Current score: 0-9.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The game will be over in another run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming towards me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:50.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:51.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:54.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:56.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice play!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:57.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000000&}- That's my buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:05.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Picking up where we left off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:05.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:06.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:10.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,During the previous incident, when you and Suzumiya-san were in the other world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...how did you make it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:13.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't remind me of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:15.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If we use that method again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:17.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...it may get us out of this crisis again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:18.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:20.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:23.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall go secure our means to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:24.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:27.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...her interests should coincide with ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:32.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato-san's finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:35.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:37.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be reciting an incantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:38.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Incantation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:40.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:41.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:42.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:45.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,An incantation, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:17:59.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you hiding that strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:04.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This has been modified with a boost in attribute data.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:05.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:06.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Homing mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That ball's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:13.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. Homing mode, is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:14.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's a limit to ridiculousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:25.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whatever the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...any more of this and we'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:29.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a variety of ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:31.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:33.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:34.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:34.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:35.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:37.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd forgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:40.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but there is a time limit of ninety minutes per game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:42.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which means the next inning will be dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:45.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we last through this inning, we'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:47.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay for us to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot afford the alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:51.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to our efforts...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:54.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the expansion of closed space has been checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:57.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But if they make a comeback now, it'll be a walk-off loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:01.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no need to think about how bad of a mood Haruhi will be in then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I have an idea concerning that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:06.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:07.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:10.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To make it through this inning while giving up a minimal number of runs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:12.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is our only remaining option.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:13.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:19.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:21.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Be serious about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:22.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I let you take my place...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:24.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so if you lose, you have to treat everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:26.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:29.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, the fate of the world rests on my pitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:32.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The world sure isn't worth much these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks to this "Mysterious Ball"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:37.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:41.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as christened by yours truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:42.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it appears we've avoided destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Strike two!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:47.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strikeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:52.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The next pitcher struck out in three pitches...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:51.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Strikeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:56.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and what would probably be the last batter had chalked up two strikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Strike two!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:56.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:58.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish it with the next pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:01.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't need you to tell me to end the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:03.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, Kamigahara Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:06.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wild pitch, Nagato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:10.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up the ball and throw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:19.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:19.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:21.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:26.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:29.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We happen to be a slightly unreasonable group.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:31.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Game over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks to Nagato's bogus magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:36.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...we've ended up winning, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:39.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do about the next game?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:41.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Continuing onto the next round...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:44.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...would be inexcusable to the Kamigahara Pirates. Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:49.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is that I need to go help my colleagues soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:51.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll be short on members, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:53.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:57.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear that it is a bad idea to allow Suzumiya-san to be bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:00.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We should take that into consideration during future endeavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:02.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had your fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:05.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi had to leave because something came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:09.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My legs and arms are completely worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:17.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's okay with you, I guess that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:19.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty hungry anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:21.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go have lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:25.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:26.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.04,0:21:29.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:31.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,About that bat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:35.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know I had it in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:35.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}So you're Yuki Nagato-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:37.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have talent for baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:37.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}I've heard a lot about you from Mikuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:39.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:41.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all Kyon's treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:43.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:46.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I managed to get my hands on some unexpected extra cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:49.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here's to the success of the Kamigahara Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:56.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! C'mon! Swing harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:02.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:03.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:05.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one do you want to do next?
